title: Sweet d'Buster Live (kro radio - febr.11 1980)
description:
Sweet d'Buster Live Concert. KRO radio-studio, Febr.11 1980. 
NL release. Dutch rockband, 70's supergroup.
Lossless WAV. Entire concert in one track. Time: 53:23 min.
